snippet.title: Game Gear - Honoo no Doukyuuji - Dodge Danpei © 1992 Sega - Gameplay
snippet.description:
DESCRIPTION
Honoo no Doukyuuji: Dodge Danpei is a Sports game, developed by SIMS and published by Sega, which was released in Japan in 1992.
